'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:10.4":{"pli":"taṃ ṭhānaṃ patthayiṃ ahaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap539:11.1":{"pli":"Tato avoca lokaggo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:11.2":{"pli":"‘passathetaṃ dijuttamaṃ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:11.3":{"pli":"Vinataṃ pādamūle me, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:11.4":{"pli":"kamalodarasappabhaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap539:12.1":{"pli":"Buddhaseṭṭhassa bhikkhussa, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:12.2":{"pli":"Ṭhānaṃ patthayate ayaṃ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:12.3":{"pli":"Tāya saddhāya cāgena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:12.4":{"pli":"Saddhammassavanena ca. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap539:13.1":{"pli":"Sabbattha sukhito hutvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:13.2":{"pli":"saṃsaritvā bhavābhave; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:13.3":{"pli":"Anāgatamhi addhāne, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:13.4":{"pli":"lacchase taṃ manorathaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap539:14.1":{"pli":"Satasahassito kappe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:14.2":{"pli":"okkākakulasambhavo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:14.3":{"pli":"Gotamo nāma gottena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:14.4":{"pli":"satthā loke bhavissati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap539:15.1":{"pli":"Tassa dhammesu dāyādo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:15.2":{"pli":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:15.3":{"pli":"Koṭṭhiko nāma nāmena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap539:15.4":{"pli":"hessati satthu sāvako’. ","htm